%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22AI%20is%20spreading%20faster%20than%20electricity%20or%20the%20internet%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20but%20half%20the%20world%20can't%20join%20in%2C%20Microsoft%20report%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Robotic%20hands%20holding%20planet%20Earth%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6904a6690be9845f2dc575b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224326%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMicrosoft%20says%20AI%20is%20spreading%20faster%20than%20any%20technology%20ever%20%E2%80%94%20but%20billions%20are%20being%20left%20behind.%3Cp%3EScience%20Photo%20Library%20via%20Reuters%20Connect%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20is%20spreading%20faster%20than%20any%20tech%20ever%2C%20but%20billions%20are%20locked%20out%2C%20Microsoft%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20tech%20giant%20warns%20the%20AI%20revolution%20could%20deepen%20global%20inequality%20without%20urgent%20investment.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMost%20AI%20models%20are%20trained%20in%20English%2C%20leaving%20billions%20unable%20to%20access%20tools%20in%20their%20language.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-ai-divide-roiling-video-game-giant-electronic-arts-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EArtificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20spreading%20faster%20than%20any%20technology%20in%20history%20%E2%80%94%20but%20billions%20of%20people%20are%20being%20left%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20conclusion%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-internal-memo-using-ai-no-longer-optional-github-copilot-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E's%20new%20%26quot%3BAI%20Diffusion%20Report%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20maps%20how%20AI%20use%2C%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20innovation%20are%20spreading%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-jobs-overlap-affect-research-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecompany%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20more%20than%201.2%20billion%20people%20now%20use%20AI%20tools%2C%20a%20rate%20of%20adoption%20that%20it%20said%20has%20outpaced%20electricity%2C%20computers%2C%20and%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20this%20rapid%20diffusion%20is%20uneven.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20revealed%20a%20widening%20gap%20between%20AI%20%26quot%3Bhaves%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bhave-nots%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20nations%20equipped%20with%20the%20power%2C%20data%2C%20and%20skills%20to%20use%20AI%2C%20and%20those%20that%20still%20lack%20the%20basics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ce60955f-c9bc-4ef2-8342-491a61a4dfcd%5C%22%3EAI's%20fastest%20spread%20ever%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20everywhere%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Microsoft%2C%20countries%20like%20the%20UAE%2C%20with%2059.4%25%20adoption%2C%20Singapore%20at%2058.6%25%2C%20and%20Norway%20at%2051.9%25%2C%20lead%20the%20world%20in%20AI%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20nations%20boast%20abundant%20electricity%2C%20near-universal%20internet%20access%2C%20and%20digitally%20fluent%20populations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20across%20parts%20of%20Sub-Saharan%20Africa%2C%20South%20Asia%2C%20and%20Latin%20America%2C%20fewer%20than%2010%25%20of%20people%20use%20AI%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20attributed%20this%20to%20low%20internet%20penetration%2C%20unreliable%20power%2C%20and%20limited%20access%20to%20the%20devices%20and%20education%20needed%20to%20use%20new%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20warned%20that%20without%20electricity%2C%20internet%2C%20and%20digital%20skills%2C%20communities%20cannot%20fully%20participate%20in%20the%20digital%20economy%20or%20benefit%20from%20new%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22376a253e-fd22-4161-8d7e-877d89be032c%5C%22%3EThe%20new%20digital%20divide%3A%20Power%2C%20not%20bandwidth%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20framed%20AI%20diffusion%20around%20three%20forces%3A%20frontier%20builders%20(who%20develop%20models)%2C%20infrastructure%20builders%20(who%20provide%20compute%20and%20data%20centers)%2C%20and%20AI%20users%20(who%20apply%20the%20tools).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20frontier%20innovation%20is%20concentrated%20in%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20and%20South%20Korea%2C%20the%20infrastructure%20gap%20is%20even%20starker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20leads%20the%20world%20with%2053.7%20gigawatts%20(GW)%20of%20data%20center%20capacity%2C%20followed%20by%20China%20with%2031.9%20GW%2C%20Germany%20with%208.5%20GW%2C%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20with%207.4%20GW.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20AI's%20spread%20depends%20on%20electricity%20and%20computing%20capacity%20as%20much%20as%20on%20algorithms%20or%20data%2C%20and%20that%20more%20than%20700%20million%20people%20still%20lack%20reliable%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b47e17e0-dfce-4dd6-982e-96d86998b907%5C%22%3EAI%20speaks%20English%2C%20and%20that's%20a%20problem%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELanguage%20is%20another%20major%20barrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20most%20large%20language%20models%20are%20primarily%20trained%20on%20English%20and%20other%20high-resource%20languages%2C%20while%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20world's%207%2C000%20languages%20are%20effectively%20absent%20from%20AI%20systems%2C%20limiting%20access%20for%20billions%20of%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELow-resource%20languages%2C%20including%20Hausa%2C%20Bengali%2C%20and%20Chichewa%2C%20are%20underrepresented%20in%20major%20AI%20models%2C%20leaving%20users%20in%20those%20regions%20to%20interact%20with%20tools%20that%20don't%20understand%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20warned%20that%20unless%20digital%20infrastructure%20and%20education%20catch%20up%2C%20%26quot%3Bthis%20gap%20will%20define%20who%20benefits%20from%20AI%20for%20decades%20to%20come%26quot%3B%20and%20could%20cement%20a%20new%20technological%20divide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20