C%20per%20Campden%20Wealth's%202025%20report.%3Cp%3EGary%20Hershorn%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f112eff5-7a93-42fb-98bf-df5774d265a3%5C%22%3ESmaller%20fortunes%20are%20getting%20in%20on%20the%20act%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20global%20survey%20by%20Julius%20Baer%20and%20PwC%20%E2%80%94%20covering%202%2C485%20wealth%20management%20and%20family%20office%20experts%20across%20Europe%2C%20Asia%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20and%20Latin%20America%20%E2%80%94%20found%20that%2041%25%20of%20ultra-high-net-worth%20respondents%20cited%20cost%20as%20the%20main%20barrier%20to%20setting%20up%20a%20single-family%20office%2C%20followed%20by%20management%20complexity%20and%20the%20belief%20that%20their%20wealth%20wasn't%20substantial%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Mosquera%20said%20those%20concerns%20are%20often%20misplaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20rise%20of%20technology%2C%20regulation%2C%20and%20global%20mobility%2C%20new%20models%20have%20emerged%20that%20allow%20smaller%20fortunes%20to%20access%20the%20same%20level%20of%20professionalism%20as%20billionaires%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20families%20prefer%20to%20keep%20control%20of%20areas%20like%20philanthropy%20or%20governance%2C%20while%20others%20prioritize%20access%20to%20specialized%20expertise%20via%20external%20partners%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIn%20reality%2C%20most%20family%20offices%20adopt%20a%20hybrid%20model%2C%20combining%20internal%20oversight%20with%20outsourced%20services%20such%20as%20legal%2C%20wealth%20planning%2C%20or%20investment%20advisory.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a9cc5c3f-8ad6-46c4-a329-fb24f6198e46%5C%22%3EHow%20smaller%20fortunes%20can%20start%20their%20own%20family%20office%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20don't%20need%20dynastic%20wealth%20to%20take%20a%20family-office%20approach%2C%20according%20to%20Julius%20Baer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20principles%20that%20once%20served%20Renaissance%20estates%20can%20be%20applied%20by%20today's%20entrepreneurs%2C%20business%20sellers%2C%20and%20globally%20mobile%20families%20%E2%80%94%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Start%20small%20and%20evolve%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMosquera%20advises%20families%20to%20view%20the%20process%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20phased%2C%20thoughtful%20evolution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20planning%20a%20business%20sale%20or%20expecting%20liquidity%20can%20begin%20by%20formalizing%20what%20they%20already%20do%20%E2%80%94%20setting%20clear%20governance%2C%20defining%20investment%20principles%2C%20and%20establishing%20communication%20routines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20single%20trusted%20advisor%20or%20accountant%20can%20act%20as%20the%20nucleus%20before%20more%20roles%20are%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Use%20hybrid%20or%20virtual%20models%20to%20stay%20lean%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Julius%20Baer%20report%20defines%20a%20Virtual%20Family%20Office%20(VFO)%20as%20%26quot%3Bideal%20for%20globally%20mobile%20families%2C%26quot%3B%20using%20%26quot%3Bdigital%20platforms%20and%20remote%20teams%20to%20deliver%20services%20flexibly%20across%20borders.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20model%20gives%20smaller%20fortunes%20the%20same%20strategic%20control%2C%20minus%20the%20heavy%20fixed%20costs%20of%20staff%20and%20office%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Outsource%20the%20complex%20%E2%80%94%20keep%20the%20core%20in-house%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Mosquera%20puts%20it%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20depends%20on%20the%20family's%20priorities%2C%20the%20complexity%20of%20their%20wealth%2C%20and%20how%20much%20operational%20infrastructure%20they%20want%20to%20oversee.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFamilies%20can%20outsource%20investment%2C%20tax%2C%20and%20legal%20matters%20while%20keeping%20philanthropy%2C%20governance%2C%20and%20education%20in-house%20%E2%80%94%20a%20structure%20that%20balances%20control%20with%20efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Choose%20jurisdiction%20wisely%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocation%20influences%20%26quot%3Beverything%20from%20stability%20and%20regulatory%20clarity%20to%20access%20to%20talent%2C%20privacy%2C%20and%20lifestyle%2C%26quot%3B%20Mosquero%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Switzerland%2C%20Singapore%2C%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20and%20Dubai%20lead%20as%20global%20hubs%2C%20Mosquera%20notes%20that%20many%20families%20now%20operate%20virtually%20%E2%80%94%20coordinating%20data%2C%20advisors%2C%20and%20decision-making%20digitally%20across%20continents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Anchor%20everything%20in%20values%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20thoughtfully%20designed%20family%20office%20often%20becomes%20the%20cornerstone%20for%20long-term%20wealth%20preservation%20and%20successful%20intergenerational%20transfer%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Thomas%20Frauenlob%2C%20member%20of%20the%20Global%20Wealth%20Management%20Committee%20and%20Co-Head%20Region%20Western%20Markets%20%26amp%3B%20Switzerland%20at%20Julius%20Baer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20anchored%20in%20these%20elements%2C%20it%20offers%20far%20greater%20value%20than%20generic%2C%20one-size-fits-all%20solutions%2C%26quot%3B%20Mosquera%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20universal%20blueprint%2C%26quot%3B%20Mosquera%20said.%20%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20the%20right%20approach%20is%20thoughtfully%20curated%20to%20reflect%20each%20family's%20unique%20needs%2C%20preferences%2C%20and%20aspirations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-smaller-fortunes-use-family-offices-to-build-lasting-wealth-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1761910395000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69048658599d46a4ccc1358a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-smaller-fortunes-use-family-offices-to-bui